fields.name: Dragon's Fury
fields.description: Dragon's Fury is a pizza that ignites the senses with its fiery blend of flavors. The spicy pepperoni, paired with tender chicken and a fiery kick of jalapenos, conjures up images of a raging dragon breathing flames in the heart of a dark dungeon. The sprinkling of red onions and blue cheese crumbles add a bold and daring edge to the pizza, as if the dragon itself has left its mark on the dish.

fields.name: Siren's Song
fields.description:
Siren's Song pizza is a bewitching combination of flavors that will have you under its spell. With a tantalizing tomato sauce base and a symphony of mozzarella, green bell peppers, and olives
This pizza's siren song will call out to you irresistibly, the combination of salty and tangy flavors, along with the vibrant colors of the toppings, create a sensory experience that will leave you mesmerized.

fields.name: Lair of the Beast
fields.description: Lair of the Beast pizza is a carnivorous delight that will satisfy the hunger of even the most ferocious appetites. Loaded with tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, and an assortment of premium meats including pepperoni, , bacon and ham. This pizza is sure to transport you to the depths of the beast's lair. Each bite is a bold and flavorful journey into the heart of the hunt, inviting you to unleash your inner carnivore and indulge in the ultimate pizza experience.

fields.name: Mystic Mushroom
fields.description: Mystic Mushroom is a pizza that will transport you to a whimsical world of magic and enchantment. The earthy and rich flavor of shiitake mushrooms, combined with the creamy and tangy taste of cream cheese and the sweetness of red onions, will make your taste buds dance. The savory tomato sauce and stretchy mozzarella cheese provide the perfect canvas for these delightful toppings.

fields.name: Ogre's breakfast
fields.description: The Ogre's Breakfast pizza is a hearty and satisfying meal fit for even the largest of appetites. With a robust tomato sauce and melty mozzarella cheese as a base, this pizza is topped with generous portions of savory sausage, perfectly cooked eggs, and flavorful red peppers. For a touch of earthiness and nutrition, fresh spinach is scattered throughout. This pizza is sure to give any ogre the energy they need to tackle their day with ferocity and vigor!

fields.name: Family Deal
fields.description:
Feed your whole family with this incredible offer!
Offer includes: 2 pizza's and 2 L beverage of your choosing.

fields.description: That non-descript orange drink that's so fizzy you'll float!

fields.name: Enchanted Ember Wings(BBQ)
fields.description: Introducing our Enchanted Ember Wings. These succulent chicken wings are infused with the essence of enchanted fire and BBQ sauce, which imbues them with a magical glow and an otherworldly flavor. Every bite of these wings is like a journey through a magical realm, with smoky and savory notes blending together in perfect harmony.

fields.name: Enchanted Ember Wings(Hot sauce)
fields.description: Introducing our Enchanted Ember Wings. These succulent chicken wings are infused with the essence of enchanted fire and hot sauce,  giving them an otherworldly flavor. Every bite of these wings is like a journey through a magical realm, with smoky and savory notes blending together in perfect harmony.

fields.name: Golden Elegance
fields.description: Indulge in the ultimate luxurious bread experience with our "Golden Elegance" breadsticks. Each golden-brown stick is infused with a delicate blend of premium herbs and spices, making for a rich, aromatic taste that will tantalize your taste buds!

fields.name: Game Night
fields.description:
Enjoy Game Night with this incredible offer!
Offer includes:
1 pizza, 1 side and 2 L beverage of your choosing

fields.name: Puff the Dragon
fields.description: Puff the Dragon is the perfect addition to any pizza lover's collection. Puff's soft, fluffy body makes it perfect for cuddling and snuggling, and its size is just right for displaying on a bed or shelf.

fields.name: Puff the Dragon - sticker
fields.description: Puff the Dragon loves nothing more than devouring a delicious pizza pie. Display your love for Puff the Dragon by posting this sticker on your laptop or other items at home!

fields.name: Pizza sticker
fields.description:
One of the Pizza Lairs delicious pizzas has come alive in this sticker, can you guess which pizza it is?
Show off your love for the Pizza Lair pizzas by displaying this sticker on your laptop or other devices!

fields.name: Pizza plushie
fields.description:
One of the pizzas from the Pizza Lair has come to life in this deliciously soft plushie!
The Pizzas soft, fluffy body makes it perfect for cuddling and snuggling, and its size is just right for displaying on a bed or shelf.

fields.name: Puff the Dragon - Onesie
fields.description:
This Puff the Dragon onesie will have you be the envy of all your friends at your next sleepover!
Show your love of the Pizza Lair by getting it now!

fields.name: Puff the Dragon - pin
fields.description:
With this Puff the Dragon pin you can show off your love for the Pizza Lair anywhere you go!
Pin it on your cap or backpack to show your friends that you are a Puff the Dragon fan!

fields.name: Pizza - pin
fields.description: Show off your love for the Pizza Lair with this pizza slice pin!

fields.name: Pizza - pin
fields.description: Show off your love of the Pizza Lair with this pizza slice pin!

fields.name: Garden Madness
fields.description: Garden Madness is a vegan's dream come true. Topped with a generous helping of flavorful vegan cheese, this pizza also features a garden's worth of fresh and tasty vegetables. You'll find juicy slices of paprika, savory mushrooms, salty olives, and zesty tomato sauce, all on top of a crispy crust. To make it even more appealing, we've added some tasty and meat-free pepperoni.

fields.name: Enchanted Dragon Fire
fields.description: This pizza is topped with spicy jalapenos, tangy tomato sauce, creamy vegan cream cheese, crispy nachos, and melty vegan cheese. The flavors blend together in a magical dance on your taste buds, transporting you to a fantastical realm of flavor and adventure!

fields.name: The Pined ham
fields.description: I can't believe you've done this.

fields.name: Inferno's Fury
fields.description: Savor the heat of our Inferno's Fury pizza! Tomato sauce and melted mozzarella cheese provide the perfect base for the spicy kick of our pepperoni. But that's not all - we've added a generous layer of sharp cheddar cheese to top it off and send your taste buds into overdrive. This fiery pizza is not for the faint of heart, but for those who dare to indulge in the flames of flavor.

fields.name: Fiery Date Night
fields.description: Fiery Date Night is a magical blend of heat and sweetness. Our signature tomato sauce and gooey mozzarella cheese perfectly complement the spicy pepperoni and fresh chili, while the cream cheese and succulent dates add a touch of decadence. This pizza is the perfect choice for those seeking adventure and a little romance in their lives.

fields.name: Vegan Combo
fields.description:
Here at Pizza Lair we appreciate our vegan friends with this combo! 
Offer includes:
1 vegan pizza of your choice and a soda

fields.name: Green Field
fields.description: Behold, the 'Green Field' pizza - a creation of pure magic and imagination. With a base of golden crust, crowned with a celestial red sauce and a blanket of vegan cheese that shimmers like stardust, this pizza is not of this world. But it is the humble cabbage, adorned in emerald green, that truly brings this pizza to life. Like a verdant field of enchanted greens, it offers a refreshing crunch and savory taste that's fit for the palate of any adventurer on a quest for flavor. Dare to indulge in this mystical creation and you'll be transported to a world where veganism reigns supreme and taste knows no bounds
